            "title": "Kiniksa Pharmaceuticals International, plc GAAP EPS of $0.27 beats by $0.09, revenue of $214.3M beats by $8.21M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Kiniksa Pharmaceuticals International, plc <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489952-kiniksa-pharmaceuticals-reports-first-quarter-2026-financial-results-and-recent-portfolio\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KNSA\" title=\"Kiniksa Pharmaceuticals International, plc\">KNSA</a></span>): Q1 GAAP EPS of $0.27 <span> beats by $0.09</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $214.3M (+55.6% Y/Y) <span> beats by $8.21M</span>.</li>\n<li>Kiniksa expects 2026 ARCALYST net product revenue of between $930 million and $945 million, compared to prior guidance of between $900 million and $920 million.</li>\n<li>Kiniksa expects its current operating plan to remain cash flow positive on an annual basis.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
